                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-83-off470 t18321129-83-cd471"></join>, 1 snuff-box, value 1s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18321129-83-victim820" type="victimName">
